MARITZBURG United have confirmed the appointment of Mabhuti Khenyeza as coach Muhsin Ertugral assistant coach. Maritzburg said on Twitter: "CLUB STATEMENT: Maritzburg United are delighted to confirm the appointment of Mabhuti Khenyeza as assistant coach to Muhsin Ertugral."Khenyeza was quoted as saying: "Becoming a coach is something I always wanted to pursue after my playing career."I have kept an eye on the club over the years, and I am really happy to start my journey here." 